OL,3,CPensioner pleads guilty to causing
OL,4,Cdeath of schoolgirl by careless driving
OL,6,FA Co Antrim pensioner today pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to causing the death last year
OL,8,Fof a school girl by careless driving.
OL,10,FJohn Noble Lindsay, 92, of Prince
OL,11,FAndrew Way, Carrickfergus, was brought
OL,12,Finto Belfast Crown Court in a
OL,13,Fwheelchair for the hearing.
OL,15,FHe originally faced one charge of
OL,16,Fcausing the death of eight-year-old
OL,17,FScarlett Rossborough by dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving on High Street in
OL,19,FCarrickfergus shortly before noon on
OL,20,FWednesday, August 9, 2023.
