OL,3,CPensioner pleads guilty to causing
OL,4,Cdeath of schoolgirl by careless driving
OL,6,FAt the request of the prosecution, a
OL,7,Fsecond charge of causing her death by
OL,8,Fcareless driving was added to the bill
OL,9,Fof indictment.
OL,11,FWhen the fresh charge was put to him,
OL,12,FMr Noble, who was allowed to remain
OL,13,Foutside the dock, replied: "I plead
OL,14,Fguilty.''
OL,16,FHe pleaded not guilty to causing the
OL,17,Fschoolgirl's death by dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving.
