OL,3,CPensioner pleads guilty to causing
OL,4,Cdeath of schoolgirl by careless driving
OL,6,FDefence counsel Frank O'Donoghue KC
OL,7,Fsaid that by entering his plea, the
OL,8,Fdefendant was not challenging the fact
OL,9,Fthat his driving caused the death of
OL,10,Fthe schoolgirl.
OL,12,F"The only issue is whether his driving
OL,13,Fis to be properly labelled in law as
OL,14,Fdangerous or careless,'' Mr O'Donoghue
OL,15,Ftold Belfast Recorder Judge Patricia
OL,16,FSmyth.
OL,18,F"We have a report from a consultant
OL,19,Fgeriatrician who comments and reports
OL,20,Fabout pedal misapplication.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
