OL,6,F"Pedal misapplication is where an
OL,7,Felderly person presses the accelerator
OL,8,Frather than the brake thinking they
OL,9,Fare pressing the brake and in this
OL,10,Fcase there are features of that.
OL,12,F"It is my intention to serve that on
OL,13,Fthe Crown in the next seven days and
OL,14,Fmake that part of the evidence in this
OL,15,Fcase.''
OL,17,FProsecution counsel David Russell KC
OL,18,Fsaid that in light of Lindsay's guilty
OL,19,Fplea, he was making a formal
OL,20,Fapplication to have the defendant
OL,21,Fdisqualified from driving.
