OL,3,CPensioner pleads guilty to causing
OL,4,Cdeath of schoolgirl by careless driving
OL,6,FSetting the trial date for the charge
OL,7,Fof causing death by dangerous driving
OL,8,Ffor November 4, 2024, Judge Smyth
OL,9,Fformally disqualified Lindsay from
OL,10,Fgetting behind the wheel.
OL,12,FThe case will be reviewed early next
OL,13,Fmonth.
OL,15,FScarlett Rossborough was from Larne
OL,16,Fwhere she attended Linn Primary School.
