OL,3,CPensioner pleads guilty to causing
OL,4,Cdeath of schoolgirl by careless driving
OL,6,FFollowing her tragic death, teachers
OL,7,Fat the school said she was "a much-
OL,8,Floved pupil" who would "always be
OL,9,Fremembered for her infectious giggles
OL,10,Fand sense of fun".
OL,12,FThe school added that Scarlett was
OL,13,Fvery popular with both staff and
OL,14,Fpupils and that she will be deeply
OL,15,Fmissed by all who knew her.
OL,17,FShe and the other children are
OL,18,Funderstood to have been out walking on
OL,19,Fa community centre's summer scheme
OL,20,Ftrip when the collision happened.
